---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 18, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — SundayRec"
  description="Terms of Service for SundayRec software and sundayrec.com"
>
  <header class="bg-[#194280] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <img src="/images/sundayrec_primary_gull-paa-blaa.svg" alt="SundayRec" class="w-10 h-10" />
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">SundayRec</span>
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-300 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-gray prose-headings:text-[#194280] prose-a:text-[#194280] max-w-none">

      <p>Please read these Terms of Service ("Terms") carefully before using SundayRec software and the sundayrec.com website ("Service"), operated by Richard Fossland ("we", "us", or "our").</p>

      <p>By downloading, installing, or using SundayRec, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.</p>

      <h2>1. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>SundayRec is audio recording software designed for churches and religious organizations. It enables automatic recording of services, editing of audio content, and distribution to podcast platforms. The Service is provided as a desktop application for macOS and Windows.</p>

      <h2>2. License</h2>
      <p>Subject to your compliance with these Terms, we grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to download and use SundayRec for your organization's internal purposes.</p>
      <p>You may not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Redistribute, sell, or sublicense the software</li>
        <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the software</li>
        <li>Use the software for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Remove or alter any proprietary notices or labels</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Free and Pro Tiers</h2>
      <p>SundayRec is available in two tiers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Free:</strong> Core recording features available at no cost, indefinitely.</li>
        <li><strong>Pro:</strong> Advanced editing and publishing features available via a paid subscription (currently kr 500 per year per church). Pro features are billed annually.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Payments</h2>
      <p>Payments for Pro subscriptions are processed by Paddle.com Market Limited ("Paddle"), who acts as the Merchant of Record for all transactions. By purchasing a Pro subscription, you also agree to <a href="https://www.paddle.com/legal/checkout-buyer-terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Paddle's buyer terms</a>. All pricing is listed excluding applicable taxes. VAT or other taxes may be added at checkout depending on your location.</p>

      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>SundayRec, its logo, and all related content are the property of Richard Fossland and protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Nothing in these Terms transfers any intellectual property rights to you.</p>

      <h2>6. User Content</h2>
      <p>You retain full ownership of all audio recordings and content you create using SundayRec. We do not access, store, or process your recordings on our servers unless you explicitly use a cloud-based feature.</p>

      <h2>7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>The Service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement. We do not warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses.</p>

      <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of data or recordings, arising from your use of or inability to use the Service.</p>

      <h2>9. Termination</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your access to Pro features at any time if you violate these Terms. Upon termination, your right to use Pro features will immediately cease. The Free tier remains available.</p>

      <h2>10. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms at any time. We will notify users of material changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

      <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Norway. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Norway.</p>

      <h2>12. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-[#0f2a54] py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-blue-300">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="/refund" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Refund Policy</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
